name: OS.01-16 @ H=N BLOCK+A
description:
This final OBJKT of the Series:'Open Structures', gets air-dropped to the first 6 Collectors that collected at least one OBJKT of each of these 4 Sets:
OS. 01-04 = OS.SetA_____key[G]
OS. 05-08 = OS.SetB_____key[H]
OS. 09-12 = OS.SetC_____key[J]
OS. 13-16 = OS.SetD_____key[K]
Holders of this OBJKT will have full access to all the unlockable content at H=N BLOCK+A.  
This series 'Open Structures', explores open configurations and variation through participation, resulting in a multi-subjective and multi-objective collaborative whole, an open architecture of collaborative objects. 
Designed at: H=N BLOCK+A, an extension patch(Architecture Kit) for H=N BLOCK, enabling realtime collaborative design using an architectural kit of parts.
